        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "When he heard them say concerning Tirhakah king of Cush, “He has come out to fight against you,” and when he heard it he sent messengers to Hezekiah, saying,"
      },
